	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64250732"><p>One of the later books in the Douglas Adams' 'Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy' series has:</p><p>'One of the many many reasons why people thought  him  insane  was because  of  the  peculiarity  of his house which, even in a land where most people's houses were peculiar in one way  or  another, was quite extreme in his peculiarness.</p><p>'His house was called The Outside of the Asylum.</p><p>'His name was simply John Watson, though he preferred to be called -  and  some  of his friends had now reluctantly agreed to this -Wonko the Sane.'</p><p>That Apple has got away with it for so long is evidence that Wonko is probably right in his designation of most of the world as an asylum for the sane.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64250732">
<span class="ind"></span><a id="reply_link_64250732" class="btn link" href="//apple.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23230944&amp;op=Reply&amp;threshold=1&amp;commentsort=0&amp;mode=thread&amp;pid=64250732" onclick="D2.replyTo(64250732); return false;">Reply to This</a> <span class="ind"></span><a class="btn link" href="//apple.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23230944&amp;threshold=1&amp;commentsort=0&amp;mode=thread&amp;cid=64250628" onclick="return D2.selectParent(64250628)">Parent</a> 	<a href="#" class="comment_share_toggle btn link">Share</a>
	<div class="comment_share sharethis-0 hide"><span class="au"></span>
